Excellent! Now I have all the information needed. Let me compile a comprehensive report:

## Express API Exploration Report

### Overview
This is a TypeScript Express.js API with in-memory data storage and posts/comments functionality. The project includes testing infrastructure with Vitest and dependencies for JWT authentication (not yet implemented).

